          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-大橋流太郎/Tāi-kiâu Liû-thài-lông]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12155.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(1)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12155.htm">祝發刊 [ CHIOK HOAT-KHAN ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">祝發刊
 
字kap文章就是上帝賞賜人特別&ecirc;恩典。親像對佇講話以及行踏，咱會得thang捌人&ecirc;款式；對佇文章咱猶原會。實在thang<span style="...<a href="artical-12155.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
